Set the following files in order to configure nginx-proxy with VIRTUAL_HOST configuration.
They will be used when 'decompose up' is run.

proxy_virtual_host.conf
proxy_virtual_host.key
proxy_virtual_host.crt
proxy_virtual_host.dhparam.pem

The default nginx-proxy settings can also be changed on a proxy wide basis using the following file:

proxy.conf

BEWARE, changing this file might effect other sites using the proxy. Try not use this file if possible.
